articles.description: Some additional details about the website
articles.contents:
About Me
My name is Joseph, I go to White Oaks Secondary School
About the Project
This is for the final project
Goals
to create an interactive graph +allow the mouse to view the date when it goes on the line graph to have multiple graphs that effectively depict the data +have four graphs, one which depicts the entire data set and 3 which depicts different time periods “This is data science” ~ Preceptor ([“Kane’s Free High School Data Science Bootcamp”])
